title: #62 - Another YouTuber Goes to Prison & Amazon Slavelike Conditions
description: On this VERY special episode of The H3 Podcast Ethan and Hila have a good old fashion top of the month with a #420 blaze it twist (not really). Together we discuss fat cat billionaires, being sucked out of an airplane windows, feeding toothpaste oreos to homeless people, and- of course- the M-word.
